<template>
  <router-view></router-view>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "App",
  components: {},
  methods: {
    changeAwnser(q_id, awnser) {
      this.alternatives = this.alternatives.map((q) =>
        q.id == q_id ? { ...q, awnser } : q
      );
    },
  },
  data() {
    return {
      alternatives: [
        {
          text: "oix2",
          id: 1,
        },
        {
          text: "oix3",
          id: 2,
        },
        {
          text: "oix4",
          id: 3,
          alternatives: [
            {
              value: 1,
              text: "x",
            },
          ],
        },
        {
          text: "oix5",
          id: 4,
        },
      ],
    };
  },
};
</script>
